snippet.title: Parse-O-Rhythm Demo Trailer!!
snippet.description:
Parse-O-Rhythm won the Winter Flowjam 2024 several months back. Since then, the game has been improved and refined in order to prepare it for a Steam presence. Today, the demo for the game releases on Steam!

You can view the game's steam page here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2988830/ParseORhythm/

If you would like to stay up to date with development and get involved with the community, you can do so on the Discord: https://discord.gg/wYs7AEZ4hb

A big thanks to everyone who is working on the project, has given feedback, or just enjoyed playing the game. This is going to be Encabulated Games's first commercial release on Steam, so there's a lot of excitement!
